OL,3,CWales to wear red in Dublin for the
OL,4,Clast time to help colour-blind fans
OL,6,FIreland and Wales will play each other
OL,7,Fin their traditional plain green and
OL,8,Fred shirts for the final time during
OL,9,Ftheir game next weekend (Saturday, 24
OL,10,FFebruary).
OL,12,FThe green-red combination can make it
OL,13,Fdifficult for people who are colour-
OL,14,Fblind to tell the difference between
OL,15,Fthe teams.
OL,17,FAround one in 12 men suffer from
OL,18,Fcolour vision deficiency (CVD) and one
OL,19,Fin 200 women.
