OL,3,CWales to wear red in Dublin for the
OL,4,Clast time to help colour-blind fans
OL,6,FWorld Rugby regulations will come into
OL,7,Fforce from January next year to try
OL,8,Fand make it easier for people with CVD
OL,9,Fto watch games.
OL,11,FThose regulations will be adopted by
OL,12,Fthe Six Nations, and all teams will
OL,13,Fneed to avoid kit clashes that could
OL,14,Fnegatively impact spectators and
OL,15,Ftelevision viewers suffering from CVD.
OL,17,FSix Nations guidance will see visiting
OL,18,Fteams asked to wear change kits where
OL,19,Fa colour match has been identified,
OL,20,Fmeaning Ireland would wear a change
OL,21,Fstrip in Cardiff next year.
