OL,3,CWales to wear red in Dublin for the
OL,4,Clast time to help colour-blind fans
OL,6,FWales' current change strip is black,
OL,7,Fwhich wouldn't help much, as colours
OL,8,Flike red and green can look too
OL,9,Fsimilar to this for someone with CVD.
OL,11,FWelsh Rugby Union chief executive Abi
OL,12,FTierney said: "Kit colour clashes do
OL,13,Fchange the way you watch a game, and I
OL,14,Fhave absolute empathy with those whose
OL,15,Fenjoyment is affected as a result.
