OL,3,CWales to wear red in Dublin for the
OL,4,Clast time to help colour-blind fans
OL,6,F"Our current alternate kit is black,
OL,7,Fand we have used green in the recent
OL,8,Fpast. Neither of these examples
OL,9,Fparticularly help with this issue, and
OL,10,Fadditionally, the colour red in Wales
OL,11,Fis not just traditional, but a part of
OL,12,Four culture.
OL,14,F"But there are other ways to work
OL,15,Faround the issues, and kits with
OL,16,Fsignificantly different designs can
OL,17,Fhelp avoid the problem too.
