OL,3,CWales to wear red in Dublin for the
OL,4,Clast time to help colour-blind fans
OL,6,F"We need to think laterally about how
OL,7,Fwe can overcome the issue ahead of
OL,8,Fnext year, perhaps not just with more
OL,9,Finventive use of colours, but in our
OL,10,Fkit designs too.
OL,12,F"If one team is in checks and the
OL,13,Fother is in stripes, for example, then
OL,14,Fcolours become pretty irrelevant, but
OL,15,Fwe are thinking hard about a solution
OL,16,Fthat works for everyone.
OL,18,F"We recognise that this is a serious
OL,19,Fissue for many fans, and we are taking
OL,20,Fit very seriously ourselves.
